e-overlay-wrap\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.motoparilla.it\/ebike\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Trilix-sunset-4-Instagram--1030x1030.png\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/www.motoparilla.it\/ebike\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Trilix-sunset-4-Instagram--1030x1030.png 1030w, https:\/\/www.motoparilla.it\/ebike\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Trilix-sunset-4-Instagram--300x300.png 300w, https:\/\/www.motoparilla.it\/ebike\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Trilix-sunset-4-Instagram--80x80.png 80w, https:\/\/www.motoparilla.it\/ebike\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Trilix-sunset-4-Instagram--768x768.png 768w, https:\/\/www.motoparilla.it\/ebike\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Trilix-sunset-4-Instagram--36x36.png 36w, https:\/\/www.motoparilla.it\/ebike\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Trilix-sunset-4-Instagram--180x180.png 180w, https:\/\/www.motoparilla.it\/ebike\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Trilix-sunset-4-Instagram--705x705.png 705w, https:\/\/www.motoparilla.it\/ebike\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Trilix-sunset-4-Instagram-.png 1080w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1030px) 100vw, 1030px\" class='avia_image' ><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1080\" class='wp-image-3954 avia-img-lazy-loading-not-3954 avia_image' src=\"https:\/\/www.motoparilla.it\/ebike\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Trilix-sunset-4-Instagram-.png\" alt='' title='Trilix sunset 4 Instagram'  itemprop=\"thumbnailUrl\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.motoparilla.it\/ebike\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Trilix-sunset-4-Instagram-.png 1080w, https:\/\/www.motoparilla.it\/ebike\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Trilix-sunset-4-Instagram--300x300.png 300w, https:\/\/www.motoparilla.it\/ebike\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Trilix-sunset-4-Instagram--1030x1030.png 1030w, https:\/\/www.motoparilla.it\/ebike\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Trilix-sunset-4-Instagram--80x80.png 80w, https:\/\/www.motoparilla.it\/ebike\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Trilix-sunset-4-Instagram--768x768.png 768w, https:\/\/www.motoparilla.it\/ebike\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Trilix-sunset-4-Instagram--36x36.png 36w, https:\/\/www.motoparilla.it\/ebike\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Trilix-sunset-4-Instagram--180x180.png 180w, https:\/\/www.motoparilla.it\/ebike\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Trilix-sunset-4-Instagram--705x705.png 705w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\" \/><\/a><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/p><\/div>\n\n<style type=\"text\/css\" data-created_by=\"avia_inline_auto\" id=\"style-css-av-aai5f-b51ca7de29d201c31aea393c47815133\">\n.flex_column.av-aai5f-b51ca7de29d201c31aea393c47815133{\nborder-radius:0px 0px 0px 0px;\n-webkit-border-radius:0px 0px 0px 0px;\n-moz-border-radius:0px 0px 0px 0px;\n}\n<\/style>\n<div class='flex_column av-aai5f-b51ca7de29d201c31aea393c47815133 av_two_fifth  avia-builder-el-10  el_after_av_one_half  el_before_av_hr  flex_column_div av-zero-column-padding column-top-margin'   ><section  class='av_textblock_section av-jv43cjek-adfbdd755073a6a3953d4a88391875da '  itemscope=\"itemscope\" itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/BlogPosting\" itemprop=\"blogPost\" ><div class='avia_textblock '  itemprop=\"text\" ><p>Electric foldable bicycles are sprouting up on city streets, on trains and busses, and in office buildings and apartment hallways for a good reason. It\u2019s hard to beat the convenience of a bike that origamis down to fit under your desk, but can also make your commute faster and easier.\u00a0 If you are not sure what makes Trilix foldable e-bike so special and unique, read on &#8230;<\/p>\n<p><u>POWER \u00a0<\/u><\/p>\n<p>Whether it\u2019s speeding over the worst hill on your commute or keeping pace with city traffic, e-bike riders are increasingly of the opinion that power rules. But, hey, watts alone don\u2019t tell a motor\u2019s story. Torque is also critical, as it tells you how much \u201coomph\u201d a motor provides. A motor with higher torque will feel more powerful and accelerate more quickly.\u00a0 In fact Trilix foldable is equipped with a second generation mid-drive motor with torque sensor that runs cool and strong in the 2 versions, 250W or the 500W, offering a torque of 70\/90 Nm. Not bad for a foldable e-bike!<\/p>\n<p><u>BATTERY<\/u><\/p>\n<p>For the battery, the stat you want to pay attention to is watt-hours (Wh). This one is easy: the bigger the number, the more juice the battery holds, and the farther you can go between charges.\u00a0 Trilix mounts a HG battery with 540 Wh, offering a range of 120 km!<\/p>\n<p><u>WHEEL SIZE <\/u><\/p>\n<p>A significant consideration for an electric foldable bike is the wheel size, because that dictates how small the bike can fold down or for what kind of terrain it\u2019s built to conquer. If you want a small foldable package, look for a bike with 16 inches wheels. With bigger wheels, a foldable bike will not have the compactness of a traditional foldable bike, but it does deliver more of that standard bike feel. Trilix is available with 16 inches Plus tires or 20 inches 2.0 tires to enjoy exploring new roads.<\/p>\n<p>THE ADVANTAGES OF A FOLDABLE E-BIKE VS A REGULAR BIKE<\/p>\n<p>STORAGE. A foldable e-bike is perfect for small apartment and condos. Nobody want to store a full sized bike in an apartment.<\/p>\n<p>SECURITY. A foldable e-bike is easy to take into workplace and put it under your desk. No need to be lock up in public areas.<\/p>\n<p>COMMUTE. A foldable e-bike has a free and unrestricted carriage on public transportation. A regular bike is too bulky for a bus or subway. It might require a permission.<\/p>\n<p>LEISURE. Toss two foldable e-bikes into a car trunk and go on adventure. A foldable bike can be safely sealed inside your car trunk: it\u2019s always secure and protected.\u00a0 Using a regular bike you have to use a roof-rack or a rear mounted cycle rack to carry your bicycle.<\/p>\n<p>ENVIRONMENT. Foldable e-bikes are used more often. So there will be more opportunities to replace carbon heavy journeys. Usage of a regular bike is usually limited to weekend or early morning ride.<\/p>\n<p>DID YOU KNOW THAT E-BIKES TURN PEOPLE INTO DAILY CYCLIST ?<\/p>\n<p>Riding an electric bicycle can be unbelievably good fun. It&#8217;s not just in the city, where zipping through the streets can make you feel alive, and it&#8217;s not just the ease at which you can ride at higher speeds for longer periods of time that often gets adrenaline junkies going.<\/p>\n<p>Trilix is the foldable e-bike that makes you fall in love with cycling, giving you smiles for miles !<\/p>\n<\/div><\/section><\/div>\n<div  class='hr av-ap9sb-b8a29b0f5905fb009ae43c73f53bbe9c hr-default  avia-builder-el-12  el_after_av_two_fifth  el_before_av_postcontent  avia-builder-el-last  '><span class='hr-inner '><span class=\"hr-inner-style\"><\/span><\/span><\/div>\n\n<div class='flex_column av-av_one_fourth-e35d4d7392d344ede5b92e9eb6686da9 av_one_fourth  avia-builder-el-14  el_after_av_postcontent  el_before_av_one_half  avia-builder-el-first  first flex_column_div '   ><\/div>\n<div class='flex_column av-av_one_half-d06667205e6186ec8414c6eb7605d406 av_one_half  avia-builder-el-15  el_after_av_one_fourth  el_before_av_one_fourth  flex_column_div '   ><div  class='av-social-sharing-box av-av_social_share-c0e1d72852788ca16d19d36cd9ef7e82 av-social-sharing-box-minimal  avia-builder-el-16  avia-builder-el-no-sibling  av-social-sharing-box-fullwidth '><div class=\"av-share-box\"><ul class=\"av-share-box-list noLightbox\"><li class='av-share-link av-social-link-facebook' ><a target=\"_blank\" aria-label=\"Condividi su Facebook\" href='https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/sharer.php?u=https:\/\/www.motoparilla.it\/ebike\/lifestile\/what-makes-foldable-e-bikes-so-special\/&#038;t=What%20makes%20foldable%20e-bikes%20so%20special%20%3F' aria-hidden='false' data-av_icon='\ue8f3' data-av_iconfont='entypo-fontello' title='' data-avia-related-tooltip='Condividi su Facebook' rel=\"noopener\"><span class='avia_hidden_link_text'>Condividi su Facebook<\/span><\/a><\/li